<subSubSection lastPageId="28" lastPageNumber="137" pageId="27" pageNumber="136" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="27.[813,1453,1767,1887]" pageId="27" pageNumber="136">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[813,965,1767,1791]" pageId="27" pageNumber="136">Description.</emphasis>
Size: apterous males: length 5.80–6.00 (
<typeStatus box="[820,915,1799,1823]" pageId="27" pageNumber="136">holotype</typeStatus>
5.88), width 2.53–2.75 (
<typeStatus box="[1186,1281,1799,1823]" pageId="27" pageNumber="136">holotype</typeStatus>
2.66); apterous females, length 5.13–5.44 (
<typeStatus box="[1110,1198,1831,1855]" pageId="27" pageNumber="136">allotype</typeStatus>
5.13), width 2.75–2.84 (
<typeStatus box="[822,910,1863,1887]" pageId="27" pageNumber="136">allotype</typeStatus>
